text: Henrik Nilsson (born 1 March 1969) is a Swedish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Skåne County
